Chaos, is a company with multiple departments to help anyone with entertainment needs. While other production houses and media firms out source to other companies, Chaos has every service you need under one roof, dealing with our staff from start to finish.  Chaos is made out of different departments covering all corners of the media. digital filmmaking, talent agency, photography, advertising, fashion, and comics/graphic novels. Another tool is the Chaos’s social network program helping to find the out what is going on with Chaos. 
       
        Chaos has done commercials for Doritos, Toys for Tots, L3GACY and Soles4Souls. Music videos for artist like, Urban Nerds, High Honor Society, M.Y.A.R.T, and Vicious Society and an award-winning documentary for Soles4Souls, “One Pair at a Time.” Chaos produces feature films, shorts, commercials, music videos, presentations, consults, ads, prints, clothing, photography, campaigns, absolutely everything.
